One way to address it would be to add the ability to specify arbitrary callbacks.
E.g. a Callback package, containing:
Callback.a = function (a) {
  // gets called whenever an "a" tag is rendered.
  if (kit.mode == "publish") {
     if (a.href is external) {
       append gif.
     }
  }
}

This needs a bit more thought (from me) though as it'd be nice to run callbacks pre and post tag.

